			<action-desc>
        <sponsor name-id="B001284">Mrs. Brooks of Indiana</sponsor> (for herself, <cosponsor name-id="P000604">Mr. Payne</cosponsor>, <cosponsor name-id="P000601">Mr. Palazzo</cosponsor>, and <cosponsor name-id="S001193">Mr. Swalwell of California</cosponsor>) introduced the following bill; which was referred to the <committee-name committee-id="HHM00">Committee on Homeland Security</committee-name>
      </action-desc>
